title: Your Guide to Cuban Fritas in Miami
text:
Updated: 5:16 p.m. Monday, Oct. 5, 2015 | Posted: 8:32 a.m. Monday, Oct. 5, 2015 Your Guide to Cuban Fritas in Miami 
Heading down to South Florida? Be sure to try a Cuban Frita — known in some circles as the Cuban hamburger. Take a look at some of the best spots to get fritas in the Miami area.
